title: Self Criticism, Overthinking & Heartbreak with Matthias J Barker
itunes:author: Joey Kidney

itunes:summary:
Are you hard on yourself? Do you have trouble stopping your thoughts from overthinking? Are you going through a heartbreak? Today I sat down with one of my favourite people, Matthias James Barker and we chatted about everything and it was really insightful for myself. Let us know what you think!
